author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-TelForceOne's chairman of management board decreases stake in company
text:
Sept 4 TelForceOne SA :
* Chairman of management board Sebastian Sawicki decreases stake in company to 1.22 percent from 6.6 percent via sale of 445,001 shares for 1 zloty per share
Source text for Eikon:
Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7993 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom)
